<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ المَوَاقِيتِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَمِيقَاتُ أَهْلِ المَدِينَةِ:</span> ذُو الحُلَيْفَةِ،<span class="c5"> وَأَهْلِ الشَّامِ وَمِصْرَ وَالمَغْرِبِ:</span> الجُحْفَةُ،<span class="c5"> وَأَهْلِ اليَمَنِ:</span> يَلَمْلَمُ،<span class="c5"> وَأَهْلِ نَجْدٍ:</span> قَرْنٌ،<span class="c5"> وَأَهْلِ المَشْرِقِ:</span> ذَاتُ عِرْقٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَهِيَ لِأَهْلِهَا، وَلِمَنْ مَرَّ عَلَيْهَا مِنْ غَيْرِهِمْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَمَنَ حَجَّ مِنْ أَهْلِ مَكَّةَ:</span> فَمِنْهَا،<span class="c5"> وَعُمْرَتُهُ:</span> مِنَ الحِلِّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَأَشْهُرُ الحَجِّ:</span> شَوَّالٌ، وَذُو القَعْدَةِ، وَعَشْرٌ مِنْ ذِي الحِجَّةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>* * *<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>